{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"34":"Clothing (Kitab Al-Libas)"},"section_detail":{"34":{"hadithnumber_first":4020,"hadithnumber_last":4158,"arabicnumber_first":4020,"arabicnumber_last":4158}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4077,"arabicnumber":4077,"text":"Amr ibn Huraith rapporte de son père : J’ai vu le Prophète ﷺ sur le minbar, il portait un turban noir et laissait pendre les deux extrémités entre ses épaules","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (1359)"}],"reference":{"book":34,"hadith":58}}]}